name: FluidTint™ Sunglasses "N-Style" + Hard Case (190 Days Money Back, 1 Year Warranty)
short_description:
FluidTint™ polarized lenses  automatically maintain the best vision in all  light conditions,  which makes them the first choice for all sight fishing activities like fly fishing and especially trout fishing.

This provides you with a true tactical advantage over fellow anglers whose vision is limited by traditional color lenses.

But there’s more.

Because FluidTint™ color-changing sunglasses adapt over the whole range of sunlight, from overcast to blue sky, you only need this one pair to be covered all year round—from dawn to dusk, in Spring, Summer, Fall, and Winter.
